---
import { coreStacks, coreLanguages } from '~/data/skills';
---
<section id="about" class="mx-auto mt-24 max-w-6xl">
  <div class="section-shell px-8 py-12 md:px-12" data-reveal>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:flex-row">
      <div class="max-w-xl flex-1">
        <h2 class="flex items-center gap-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-white md:text-4xl">
          <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10">
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:account-badge-outline" width="18" height="18" class="text-white/80"></iconify-icon>
          </span>
          About
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base text-white/70">
          I'm George Nizoridis— an Analytics Engineer in Melbourne. I build end‑to‑end data solutions in Microsoft Fabric
          (dataflows, pipelines, lakehouses), design and deliver Power BI reports with strong UX, and develop ML/LLM tools that deliver actionable insights and improve workflows.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-white/70">
          At Service Stream, I have pioneered Microsoft Fabric Medallion architecture, developed automated ETL pipelines, and designed and delivered over 20 production Power BI reports in regular use by the company.
          Furthermore, I have recieved an innovation award for deploying the first LLM powered solution in the company.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-white/70">
          Beyond work, I avidly take part in many endeavours, including Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, Musical Instruments (Piano and Guitar), Video games, reading, 3D Engineering (CAD, Blender, 3D Printing), and Homelabbing with my own server.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/60">What I Focus On</h3>
          <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
            {coreStacks.map((stack) => (
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
                <p class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white">
                  <span aria-hidden="true">{stack.label.includes('Machine') ? '🤖' : stack.label.includes('Analytics') || stack.label.includes('BI') ? '📊' : stack.label.includes('Data') ? '🗂️' : '🧰'}</span>
                  {stack.label}
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-xs text-white/70">
                  {stack.tools.map((tool) => (
                    <li>• {tool}</li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/60">Core Languages</h3>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-white/70">
            {coreLanguages.map((item) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1">{item === 'Python' ? '🐍 Python' : item === 'SQL' ? '🧮 SQL' : '🎮 Godot/GDScript'}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
